{"tid":1341534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"...又激一激市民下星期再出嚟","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:54:11.000Z","uid":222747,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a0cc883b682ea0dec9f3155cfdba1eb0ab971e","tid":1341534,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:46:56.000Z","msg":"本身喺中聯辦做到嘢大家都鼓舞，可能有 d 溫和嘅會覺得夠哂數收貨<br />\n但...<br />\n19：15先叫做包圍咗中聯辦，20：09就話清場,呢個速度真係高效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後幾個鐘扔煙扔彈開槍呢啲可能大家都開始麻木，但其實仍然屬於<span style=\"color: red;\">過份武力</span>嚟。<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190721&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59847817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190721%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59847817&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=3031f96f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190721%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59847817&h=9c4f59f5\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190721&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59847817</a><br />\n當然今晚個重點完美轉移咗去元朗果邊&hellip;...鄉事佬真係做到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無差別打市民，記者，議員，之前係得警察做到，而家多一個集團做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嚴重暴力事件，仲要班人係下晝已經開始集結，警察都要差唔多半個鐘先到現場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞咗咁耐先得十幾廿個警察到場，到場果陣咁啱d 白衫人走哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又唔見繼續追㗎啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有市民報警被cut 線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼沙田街坊，而家到元朗街坊we connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港鐵CCTV 咁多，我諗唔會咁啱壞哂掛，咁都拉唔到人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家可以估下未來日子拉到幾多個白衫人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日政府回應會講&ldquo;強烈譴責暴力&rdquo;呀可？咁唔該交代下警方做法是否恰當？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真我諗唔到政府點兜先可以平息到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">當然其實係冇一次平息到</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190721&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59847882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190721%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59847882&d=YI7gf4cr217w6pzPHhIkRajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=d0edef92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190721%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59847882&h=3bb0ebe8\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190721&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59847882</a>"},{"pid":"03a730d97a16f1a6e8e18c2c9b69dcbbe53c5948","tid":1341534,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:49:44.000Z","msg":"加埋警署關門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eac29047dd51564a4e0ca4e09c3580de64d5579","tid":1341534,"uid":222747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9545bf471f88786b049ce71965eb24e32524cfd","tid":1341534,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:54:11.000Z","msg":"屌，真係好嬲！<br />\n逼港鐵拎cctv出黎<br />\n逼黑警做嘢，當然哋一定放水。<br />\n星六我哋自己做嘢<br />\n光復元朗"}]}